      News story
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    The Secretary of State has reappointed Dame Judith Macgregor as Trustee of the British Tourist Authority.
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Dame Judith Macgregor has been reappointed by the Secretary of State for Digital, Culture, Media and Sport as Trustee of the British Tourist Authority for three years from 1 December 2020 to 31 November 2023.</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
